			"https://givebutter.s3.amazonaws.com/media/2e0LtvhBez1xq6Y11of6WbD6FJrJlShUPpg4jklT.png",
		campaignCoverEmbedUrl: null,
		campaignDescription:
			'<h1>CIMI Mask Making Project</h1>\n\n\t\t\t\t<p><em><span style="color: #999999"><strong>Helping CIMI Member Weather the COVID-19 Economy</strong></span></em></p>\n<p><span style="color: #ee0000"><strong>-- August 3, 2020</strong></span></p>\n<img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/77c0fc_5a5a83a669eb4a0d8611d09a538d8872~mv2.png" alt=""/>\n<p><span style="color: #000000"><strong>CIMI launched a mask-making pilot project in May 2020 to provide a family in the CIMI community with a way to earn some money during COVID-19 . CIMI bought a sewing machine and other supplies such as fabric, elastic, and scissors. Socorro was a homemaker with no experience in sewing, but she quickly learned how to make different types of masks with the help from a CIMI volunteer and Internet resources. So far she has made 180 masks and sells them for $5 each. She uses half of the money to restock on supplies to make new masks. </strong></span></p>\n<p></p>\n<img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/77c0fc_b33afe3683f24ae3a4d12e4ce40606cd~mv2.png" alt=""/>\n<p></p>\n<img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/77c0fc_8ce590d8096849d38d676f58caae705b~mv2.png" alt=""/>\n<p></p>\n<img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/77c0fc_217f46c567534ccdbc1a9b6e5e3de3aa~mv2.png" alt=""/>\n<p></p>\n<img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/77c0fc_67492b3e9c904e5ca2a32981620c7af6~mv2.png" alt=""/>\n<p></p>\n<img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/77c0fc_de5df0e413d14f6fa82bf8c084cb2050~mv2.png" alt=""/>\n<p></p>\n<img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/77c0fc_3cf2fc6fb3d349dfb4e54d987f8bc71b~mv2.png" alt=""/>\n<p><span style="color: #000000"><strong>If you’re inclined, you can support Socorro and her family by buying her masks for $5 each.</strong></span></p>',
		campaignDescriptionSimplified:
			"CIMI Mask Making Project Helping CIMI Member Weather the COVID-19 Economy -- August 3, 2020 CIMI launched a mask-making pilot project in May 2020 to provide a family in the CIMI community with a way to earn some money during COVID-19 . CIMI bought a sewing machine and other supplies such as fabric, elastic, and scissors. Socorro was a homemaker with no experience in sewing, but she quickly learned how to make different types of masks with the help from a CIMI volunteer and Internet resources. So far she has made 180 masks and sells them for $5 each. She uses half of the money to restock on supplies to make new masks. If you’re inclined, you can support Socorro and her family by buying her masks for $5 each.",
